BT /F1 11 Tf 72 659.4 Td (separately as an open data descriptor; that release is descriptive, makes no predictive claim,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 644.6 Td (and needs no pre-registration.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 624.8 Td (This is the self-contained version of the pre-registration, the one we upload to OSF Registries) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 610 Td (and timestamp. It restates every definition the design depends on, so a reader needs nothing else) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 595.2 Td (to evaluate it. The internal working copy is preregistration.md. The positioning brief it draws) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 580.4 Td (from is ../../AI_ECONOMIC_IMPACT_2026.md.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 560.6 Td (Status: drafted and self-contained. Pending co-author sign-off, then post to OSF. We have not) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 545.8 Td (accessed the outcome data. See section 2.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13.5 Tf 72 513 Td (0. Administrative) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 492 Td (-   Title. Do AI-Exposed Workers Show Financial Stress First? A State by Occupation) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 477.5 Td (    Leading-Indicator Approach.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 463 Td (-   Authors. [names, affiliations, ORCIDs to fill in]) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 448.5 Td (-   Corresponding author. [fill in]) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 434 Td (-   Version. v1 draft. Date set on posting.) Tj ET
